  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA272-kiḷavi">1. itu varaiyātu neṭuṅkālam vantoḻuka vāṟṟāḷāya talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
            2. tōḻi talaimakaṭkuc colluvāḷāyt talaimakaṉ kēṭpac colliyatūumām.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">1. What SHE said who was unable to bear it when [HE] kept coming for a long time without marrying. 2. It is also what the confidante said as one who is speaking to HER so that HE would hear it.</p>
        </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA272">
<l>            kaṭalaṅ kākkaic cevvāyc cēval</l>
<l>            paṭiva makaḷir koṭikoy taḻitta</l>
<l>            pomma laṭumpiṉ veṇmaṇa loruciṟaik</l>
<l>            kaṭuñcūl vatinta kāmar pēṭaik</l>
<l>            kiruñcēṟ ṟayirai tēriya teṇkaḻip </l>
<l>            pūvuṭaik kuṭṭan tuḻavun tuṟaiva</l>
<l>            ṉalkā maiyi ṉacaipaḻu tākap</l>
<l>            peruṅkai yaṟṟa ciṟumai yalarvā</l>
<l>            yampaṉ mūtū raṟintatu</l>
<l>            nōyā kiṉṟatu nōyiṉum peritē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Since [my] yearning became false with the decline</l>
<l rend="indent">of the man from the ghat,</l>
<l rend="indent4">where the red-beaked male</l>
<l rend="indent3">of the sea crow stirs the flowery pond</l>
<l rend="indent3">by the clear backwaters to search for Ayirai fish in the dark mud</l>
<l rend="indent3">for [its] desirable female abiding in high pregnancy</l>
<l rend="indent2">on one side of the white sands with thick Aṭumpus,</l>
<l rend="indent2">ruined since women [engaged in] austerity plucked the creepers,</l>
<l>the talkative old village’s knowing it,</l>
<l rend="indent">with mouths gossiping about [my] lowness,</l>
<l rend="indent">that has become fully motionless,</l>
<l>became pain greater than pain.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
